{"tid":599613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選最好踩既共享單車","createTime":"2018-03-20T14:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T08:28:56.000Z","uid":125303,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b7bd945859b1ddbec02a3317168c8d320228aac0","tid":599613,"uid":125303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"暫時只係踩過Hoba同埋ofo<br />\n雖然ofo有得轉波 但係成架車好似唔識去咁 <br />\n不過見佢有10分鐘內免費 用黎駁腳唔錯<br />\nofo相對輕腳 但上斜一樣辛苦 3月有5點至10點免費 駁腳又係一流<br />\n<br />\n暫時見到以下既共享單車<br />\n1. Gobee (綠)<br />\n2. Hoba (白)<br />\n3. ofo (黃)<br />\n4. Ioco (藍)<br />\n5. ketchup (黑)<br />\n6. obike (銀)"},{"pid":"0a3f06fdae068f2aeeb09fd79cdf50eda0663db3","tid":599613,"uid":125303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Hoba有得轉波先岩"},{"pid":"cd1cec9f259a631a821f29355596929743114aec","tid":599613,"uid":41678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"淨係講ofo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225ae8c4605bbf79ffa1fdc6faa296244c4e6d2b","tid":599613,"uid":125303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd1cec9f259a631a821f29355596929743114aec","tid":599613,"uid":41678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"淨係講ofo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"打錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠<br />\n只係試過hoba同ofo"},{"pid":"d79bd5f75210498198d79f7b7d6bc1c136f9f16b","tid":599613,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"Gobee OFO 可以接受 唔難踩<br />\nOBike都唔錯 但按金同租比較貴<br />\nloco踩落架單車好重 好大力先踩得郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe6c33fb84300fbd13766511dca717e1fd9cb60","tid":599613,"uid":125303,"like":0,"d